<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Subscription Expiration Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: auto;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

            ul li {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3c6b46;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Your Ghost Subscription is Expiring Soon! </h2>
        <p>Hi <strong>@Model.MemberName</strong>,</p>
        <p>Your subscription to <strong>@Model.SubscriptionTier</strong> will expire on <strong>@Model.ExpirationDate</strong>.</p>

        <h3>Why Renew? 🤔</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Continue accessing premium content</li>
            <li>✅ Stay connected with our exclusive community</li>
            <li>✅ Enjoy uninterrupted benefits</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Click the button below to renew your subscription now:</p>


        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="@Model.SubscriptionUrl" class="button">Renew Your Subscription</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us. We're here to help!</p>

        <p class="footer">
            Best,<br>
            <strong>@Model.StoreName</strong><br>
            <a href=@Model.ApiUrl>@Model.ApiUrl</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
